  <summary>3/5/1987--Introduced.
Brings within the scope of Federal motor carrier safety regulation certain commercial motor vehicles operating in a municipality or its commercial zone. Declares certain Department of Transportation regulations exempting such vehicles from Federal safety regulation to be without effect.</summary>
